This is a "Lock" demo for the feature FSM (Finite State Machine) of Akka.

See: http://cntt.tv/nodes/show/559

To run:

1. Checkout using Git and compile using SBT

cd /tmp
git clone http://github.com/ngocdaothanh/lock-fsm-akka.git
cd lock-fsm-akka
sbt update
sbt compile
sbt console

2. From the console, run

import se.scalablesolutions.akka.actor.Actor
import demo.{Lock, Button}
val l = Actor.actorOf(new Lock("2010"))
l.start
l ! Button('2')
l ! Button('0')
l ! Button('1')
l ! Button('0')
l.stop
exit
